Author: quietlyinteresting
Text: That is a along fast. I would advise you get ready for the bounce. When you eat again. Your body will be screening for fats, sugars and carbohydrates.    I know I am probably telling you something you already know but your body will be in a super hypertension state. Maybe be ready for some hard stool and faintness.
